Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: moleculer-client
Version: 0.1.6
Summary: Simple Client in python to communicate with MoleculerJs Microservices using NATS
Home-page: https://github.com/CaioFilus/moleculer-client
Author: Caio Filus Felisbino
Author-email: caio.filus@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: Simple Client in python to communicate with MoleculerJs Microservices using NATS.
        
        ## Example
        
        ```
        from moleculer_client import MoleculerClient
        
        moleculer = MoleculerClient(node_id='python-node', moleculer_nodeID="node-1", url='nats://127.0.0.1:4222')
        print(moleculer.discover())
        moleculer.emit('client.alive')
        print(moleculer.call('microservice.action', {'data': 'moleculer test'}))
        ```
Keywords: python,microservices,NATs
Platform: UNKNOWN
